ActAccess to Information Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Access to Information Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the ACCESS TO INFORMATION REGULATIONS in order to allow federal departments and agencies to be in a better position to collect and exchange information with other federal entities and to protect this information in the context of access to information requests submitted pursuant to either act.
